---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <div class="prose prose-lg">
            <p class="text-[#1d1d1f]">Last updated: December 29, 2024</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Privacy Commitment</h2>
            <p>At EmojiUtils, we prioritize your privacy and security above all else.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Data Storage and Security</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                <li>All cryptographic keys are stored securely in your device's Keychain and hashed on the database</li>
                <li>Identity verification is handled through our secure server</li>
                <li>We do not share or sell any personal information</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Server Usage</h2>
            <p>While we maintain a server for identity management, we do not store or share any personal data. The server's sole purpose is to facilitate secure identity verification.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Data Collection</h2>
            <p>EmojiUtils does not collect any personal information or analytics. We maintain only the minimum necessary data for identity verification functionality.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Your Control</h2>
            <p>You have control over your local device data and identity information. While the app uses a secure server for identity verification, your sensitive cryptographic data is stored locally on your device. You can manage your identities through the app's interface at any time.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about our privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@nichokas.us.kg" class="text-[#0066CC]">privacy@nichokas.us.kg</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>